snippet.title: Beatrect Game Play (Into Beatrect - Expert)
snippet.description:
Welcome to the official gameplay video of BeatRect, the ultimate VR rhythm game! 🎶🚀

Immerse yourself in stunning ray-traced graphics and groove to incredible tracks from renowned artists like bluestahli, celldweller, and かめりあ (Camellia). Get ready to experience VR gaming like never before!

🔗 Join our Discord community: https://discord.com/invite/2qXxK2nNzJ

💿 Add BeatRect to your Steam wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1669880/Beatrect/

Stay tuned for more updates and exciting news. Thank you for your support! 🎮✨
